終審有類似案例做指引,<br />\n當同本地法例有抵觸, 又有犯罪成份, 咁會以本地刑事法處理<br />\n<br />\n更重要問題係<br />\n而家睇到集結定義只會影響量刑嚴重程度,<br />\n而點睇, 抽到幾細, 點雞蛋入面挑骨頭, 都係審個班人話事<br />\n即係我可以放大嚴重部分黎講, 再縮細影響輕微部分<br />\n去重判一個敵人"},{"pid":"80f32c442820c98a3b8893949a020ea1f8206132","tid":2310442,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"001c00547e8005429f9ac8ca5273467a016b5410","tid":2310442,"uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:18:53.000Z","msg":"主審法官：<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">高等法院首席法官潘兆初<br />\n高等法院上訴法庭法官彭偉昌<br />\n高等法院原訟法庭法官潘敏琦</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">上訴法庭法官彭偉昌頒發上訴法庭判案理由書：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=132229&amp;currpage=T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fju%2Fju_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D132229%26currpage%3DT&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPRZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=7d51c483\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=132229&amp;currpage=T</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T12:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c7568dc7c60d96e2bae14efb36e61c6b821804","tid":2310442,"uid":178930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"469793fa9c184e027088ea021d61e7c4320d83d5","tid":2310442,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd563956f36e7f7f861d869c851ac38ee8fed33f","tid":2310442,"uid":178930,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2fe674a2740d6d46a09243abf8eaece0917af904","tid":2310442,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:30:50.000Z","msg":"可以㗎<br />\n有咩問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:36:28.000Z","msg":"講就兇狠喇你老尾<br />\n匿喺電腦前面講乜都得喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:39:36.000Z","msg":"吓又屈？<br />\n我可能已經會坐得多過三個月呢<br />\n咁你唔好匿